{"tid":122767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死3隻]餐館煤氣罐爆炸　大火奪3員工性命","createTime":"2017-02-16T10:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T12:59:28.000Z","uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80f22dc9d9aa371b85816a14b8703336e22e49a5","tid":122767,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170216/bkncn-20170216031412065-0216_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170216%2Fbkncn-20170216031412065-0216_05011_001.html&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=11f13ce5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170216/bkncn-20170216031412065-0216_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n上海虹口區汶水東路一間餐館昨早9時18分左右發生火警，導致餐館內3名員工死亡。事發後消防人員迅速趕到現場，約於9時50分將火撲滅。事後受火警影響的居民均已疏散，並獲妥善安置。<br />\n<br />\n據當地網民透露，涉事餐館經營牛肉麵，疑是煤氣罐發生爆炸引起火災，而且餐館的廚房很小，難以逃生。惟上述消息未得到官方證實，當地警方仍在調查起火原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ce21a39f4032f45df7ca0ae60ad81831259576","tid":122767,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:24:38.000Z","msg":"幾時到港畜死<br />\n港畜死左我開POST熱烈慶祝<br />\n會唔會好似台灣一樣比人拉<br />\n然後告我不誠實使用電腦罪"},{"pid":"94de6fb634daf3f36b556235a28b6aa1edb62dfe","tid":122767,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:24:38.000Z","msg":"幾時到港畜死<br />\n港畜死左我開POST熱烈慶祝<br />\n會唔會好似台灣一樣比人拉<br />\n然後告我不誠實使用電腦罪"},{"pid":"e208513c98c5d702b2526ec244f56508e5908354","tid":122767,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:24:38.000Z","msg":"幾時到港畜死<br />\n港畜死左我開POST熱烈慶祝<br />\n會唔會好似台灣一樣比人拉<br />\n然後告我不誠實使用電腦罪"},{"pid":"2dd7945ec51703cff7ba3085a8300c7e16afb3c0","tid":122767,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img s